{"tid":111364,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[港女文慎入] 理想男友 的10個特質！遇到請珍惜","createTime":"2017-02-07T11:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T12:53:59.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5faca0197f88a60d5586aae477f73ead54b1c2c9","tid":111364,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"理想男友 的10個特質！遇到請珍惜<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nmplus.hk/social-buzz/%e7%90%86%e6%83%b3%e7%94%b7%e5%8f%8b-%e7%9a%8410%e5%80%8b%e7%89%b9%e8%b3%aa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nmplus.hk%2Fsocial-buzz%2F%25e7%2590%2586%25e6%2583%25b3%25e7%2594%25b7%25e5%258f%258b-%25e7%259a%258410%25e5%2580%258b%25e7%2589%25b9%25e8%25b3%25aa%2F&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=06f57da3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nmplus.hk/social-buzz/%e7%90%86%e6%83%b3%e7%94%b7%e5%8f%8b-%e7%9a%8410%e5%80%8b%e7%89%b9%e8%b3%aa/</a><br />\n<br />\n相信不少女生都有向閨蜜大吐苦水，投訴男朋友的經驗！不外乎是男朋友不夠細心，男朋友總是很忙，男朋友太花心經常撩女仔，男朋友又&hellip;&hellip;成世流流長，總會愛上幾個人渣。在你心目中， 理想男友 要具備甚麼條件？小編首推以下10種 理想男友 的特質，「絲打」們遇到這種絕世好男人一定要好好珍惜，「mark實」私有化！"},{"pid":"6401089ff30e1fb09b5706cdf1c2d15272dddf62","tid":111364,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"不外乎高富帥專一浪漫5點姐"},{"pid":"3ce5bf920e462b39a551a53f74fd966c9da77142","tid":111364,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"理想男友的10個特質<br />\n<br />\n1&gt;起床、睡前都會想起你<br />\n<br />\n有男朋友講早晨的morning就是good morning！理想男友不論起床，抑或睡前都會想起你，早上會主動跟你講早晨，晚上睡前跟你說晚安，女朋友甜入心。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-95.jpg&h=31d7ffde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2&gt;主動報告行蹤<br />\n<br />\n正所謂「10個男人9個滾，剩返1個仲諗緊」，不少女生談戀愛都缺乏安全感，理想男友就會主動報告行蹤，放工即call，不會玩失蹤，令女朋友放心又安心。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-78.jpg&h=6210319d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3&gt;行街拖實<br />\n<br />\n試過跟男朋友拍拖走失了嗎？我朋友試過！我朋友試過！我朋友試過（我的朋友不是我）！理想男友跟你拍拖定必拖實女朋友，即使在人潮洶湧的地方，也絕不會失散。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-113.jpg&h=17f059f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4&gt;生病時照顧你<br />\n生病時，有男朋友照顧令人陪感窩心。理想男友會關心女朋友的病情，貼心照顧，伴侶左右，即使有工作，亦會定時提醒女朋友食藥，放工後人肉速遞外賣，甚至煲「愛心粥」！<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-85.jpg&h=26aceb9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5&gt;用心幫你影靚相<br />\n<br />\n最近很多女性朋友投訴另一半不懂拍照，亦不用心幫自己拍美照，即使有美景襯托，也hea影，把自己拍得很醜，真的自拍好過！理想男友會花心機幫女朋友影靚相，絕不敷衍求其！<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-115.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-115.jpg&h=d19f5074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6&gt;迅速保護你<br />\n<br />\n理想男友絕不會讓女朋友處於危險當中，人多擠迫時輕擁你，行街時會把妳拉回馬路內側，有突發情況會迅速保護你。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-39.jpg&h=f356600f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7&gt;花時間陪你<br />\n<br />\nTalk is cheap. Actions are everything. 講多無謂，行動最實際！時間比金錢更寶貴，即使口講多愛你，不花時間與妳相處都是廢的。即使工作夕忙，理想男友都會花時間跟你傾電話、whatsapp及拍拖，不會令你感到孤單。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-48.jpg&h=5b9d0d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8&gt;留意你的period<br />\n<br />\n理想男友會留意女朋友幾時m到，period期間禁止你喝冷飲、吃雪糕，甚至為你準備紅豆水。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/-28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F-28.jpg&h=288774d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9&gt;懂得避忌<br />\n<br />\n有女朋友當然不代表要跟異性朋友斷絕來往，但理想男友會懂得避忌、檢點，不會常常單獨與異性朋友在一起，會尊重你的感受。<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F08%2F207.jpg&h=09f4949d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"503c3e5707ad8483f590e72895b97d22e6844064","tid":111364,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"10&gt;拒絕AA制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不跟你計較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不介意多付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，理想男友就是不捨得讓女朋友花錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。當然男朋友大方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，自己也不會當成「老奉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」，會為對方付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"1517b5d2b7b3a6cae3b27b4744c2ec60399d3039","tid":111364,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10&gt;拒絕AA制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg